---
---

<section id="selection-process" class="bg-slate-50 py-20 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Decorative Vector Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none z-0">
        <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] text-blue-200/40 blur-3xl opacity-50 -translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M47.7,-57.2C59.4,-47.3,64.9,-29.3,67.6,-11.1C70.3,7.1,70.2,25.6,61.8,40.1C53.4,54.6,36.7,65.1,18.7,70.6C0.7,76.1,-18.6,76.6,-35.1,69.5C-51.6,62.4,-65.4,47.7,-72.1,30.3C-78.8,12.9,-78.4,-7.2,-70.6,-23.7C-62.8,-40.2,-47.6,-53.1,-32,-61.7C-16.4,-70.3,2.4,-74.6,20.1,-70.1C37.8,-65.6,56,-45,-47.7,-57.2Z" transform="translate(100 100) scale(1.1)"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="max-[min(100vw,768px)] max-w-screen-xl mx-auto fade-in-up relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-4 tracking-tight">Tahapan Seleksi</h2>
            <p class="text-subtle text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Pahami setiap tahapan agar Anda tidak melewatkan kesempatan emas ini.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14">
            <!-- Coding Camp Process -->
            <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-300 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden group/card">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-transparent via-blue-50/30 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover/card:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 z-0"></div>
                <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                     <div class="h-10 w-2.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
                     <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 tracking-tight">Coding Camp 2.0</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-10 relative mt-8">
                     <!-- Connection line with animation -->
                     <div class="absolute left-[1.15rem] top-10 bottom-10 w-1 bg-slate-100 hidden sm:block rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                         <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400 via-blue-600 to-transparent -translate-y-full group-hover/card:animate-[slideDown_3s_ease-in-out_infinite]"></div>
                     </div>
                     
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/20 bg-white text-primary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:shadow-blue-200">1</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Isi Formulir Aplikasi</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Lengkapi formulir pendaftaran dengan data diri Anda secara lengkap dan benar. Pastikan untuk meninjau kembali seluruh informasi sebelum mengirimkan formulir.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/20 bg-white text-primary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:shadow-blue-200">2</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Akses Kelas & Syarat Administrasi</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium mb-3">Setelah berhasil melakukan pendaftaran, Anda akan mendapatkan:</p>
                            <ul class="list-none text-subtle font-medium text-sm space-y-2">
                                <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>Akses ke Kelas Financial Literacy yang harus diselesaikan sebagai persyaratan administrasi.</li>
                                <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>Akses ke Kelas Dasar-Pemula sesuai Alur Belajar yang dipilih.</li>
                                <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>Akses ke Kelas Softskill Belajar Strategi Pengembangan Diri.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/20 bg-white text-primary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:shadow-blue-200">3</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Pengumuman Level Lanjutan</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Tahap terakhir ini akan memberikan Anda informasi mengenai hasil pengumuman di level lanjutan yang terdiri dari beberapa Batch.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- METC Process -->
            <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:border-purple-300 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden group/card">
                 <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-transparent via-purple-50/30 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover/card:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 z-0"></div>
                 <div class="relative z-10">
                 <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                     <div class="h-10 w-2.5 bg-secondary rounded-full"></div>
                     <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 tracking-tight">METC</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-10 relative mt-8">
                     <!-- Connection line with animation -->
                     <div class="absolute left-[1.15rem] top-10 bottom-10 w-1 bg-slate-100 hidden sm:block rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                         <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-400 via-indigo-600 to-transparent -translate-y-full group-hover/card:animate-[slideDown_3s_ease-in-out_infinite] animation-delay-500"></div>
                     </div>
                     
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary/20 bg-white text-secondary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:shadow-purple-200">1</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Pendaftaran Awal</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Lakukan registrasi di halaman program METC menggunakan akun Dicoding Anda untuk menyatakan minat dan kesediaan.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary/20 bg-white text-secondary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:shadow-purple-200">2</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pb-2">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Undangan Aktivitas Berkala</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Sesuai dengan ketersediaan kegiatan (Self-learning, Workshop, atau Hackathon), Anda akan menerima undangan via email.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex relative group">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-6 relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary/20 bg-white text-secondary font-bold shrink-0 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md group-hover:shadow-purple-200">3</div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Sertifikasi & Rewards</h4>
                            <p class="text-subtle font-medium leading-relaxed">Selesaikan misi atau event untuk mendapatkan Badge of Completion, Sertifikat, dan kesempatan memenangkan berbagai rewards.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes slideDown {
        0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
        50% { transform: translateY(100%); }
        100% { transform: translateY(100%); }
    }
    .animation-delay-500 {
        animation-delay: 0.5s;
    }
</style>
